<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_3ab8f3ef-d9fb-4016-97dc-1dfbdc7b1198" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/><facet building="Class 8"/></meta><sptc>B1D6</sptc><title id="_5223f051-d1e5-44b0-8821-b91e7291b7e5">Construction of buildings in flood hazard areas</title><archive-num>2019: B1.6</archive-num><clause-variation variation="SA" variation-type="DELETE">SA DELETE Clause</clause-variation><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1886_1.2.0.xml" variation="VIC" variation-type="REPLACE">VIC REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><clause-variation deleted-text="Building work in designated flood hazard areas is regulated by the Building Act 1975, and the Queensland Development Code 3.5 - Construction of buildings in flood hazard areas." variation="QLD" variation-type="DELETE">QLD DELETE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_cb6c1738-a930-4ae0-ba79-d03e74c68188" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_010a4d5c-3c8a-455a-ab85-6b2fbae68f08">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1308_2.0.0.xml#_3220782b-f892-4b44-a260-95123b7a9ed0" id="_9139ed20-d4eb-49b1-92b4-bc9271a25ae7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">flood hazard area</xref> must comply with the ABCB Standard for Construction of Buildings in Flood Hazard Areas.</p></subclause><subclause id="_7fa7d4a0-e6d1-42e8-8eda-c7c88fcd001a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_6132e1ed-8f42-44d6-bb01-0b5f5346dfff">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The requirements of (1) only apply to a Class 2 or 3 building, Class 9a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1333_0.4.0.xml#_1f5fbee8-584a-4244-9286-ebf9d8ebb04a" id="_40fb0fc1-1cc9-40e8-8a56-dd278ecae542" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">health-care building</xref>, Class 9c building or a Class 4 part of a building.</p></subclause></clause>